INSERT  INTO dbo.ORDRPUSH2COM
    (
         DocEntry
       , PushStatus
       , APIErr
       , U_CompCod
       , DocEntryB1
       , CreateDate
       , Type
       , U_Tmoney
       , ShopCode
       , DocType
       , Disperct
       , DocStatus
       , Type_ReturnSO
       , Phone
       , U_DocSplit
       , IDFormDK
       , U_NuBill
	)
SELECT
	  DocEntry
	, 1
	, ''
	, U_ComTo
	, NULL
	, GETDATE()
	, NULL
	, U_TMonBi
	, U_ShpCod
	, DocType
	, NULL
	, DocStatus
	, Type_ReturnSO
	, LicTradNum
	, U_DocSplit
	, IDFormDK
	, U_NuBill
FROM
    dbo.ORDR (NOLOCK)
WHERE
    DocEntry = $CURSOR$;
